<p>## 17. ENTITY RELATIONSHIP DIAGRAM (ERD)</p>
<p>The ERD illustrates the relationships among the Users, Books, Members, Book_Issue, Book_Return, and Fine tables, depicting how they interact within the Library Management System.&nbsp;</p>
<p>1. **Users** can borrow multiple **Books**.<br>2. Each **Book** can be issued multiple times but is linked to one **User** at a time.<br>3. Each **Issue** will relate to one **Return**.<br>4. Each **Book** can incur multiple **Fines**.</p>
<p>*Insert ERD diagram here for visual representation.*</p>
