<p>## 19. FLOWCHARTS</p>
<p>### Login Process<br>1. User fills credentials.<br>2. System validates user info.<br>3. If valid, redirect to dashboard; else, show error.</p>
<p>### Book Issue<br>1. User selects a book.<br>2. System checks availability.<br>3. If available, mark as issued; else, show unavailable message.</p>
<p>### Book Return<br>1. User selects a book to return.<br>2. System records return date.<br>3. Calculate any fines incurred.</p>
<p>### Fine Calculation<br>1. Compare return date with due date.<br>2. If overdue, compute fines based on days overdue.</p>
<p>*Insert flowcharts for each process.*</p>
